Vehicle Movement

User  is asked to choose among the registered vehicle and already added locations(where cameras has also been installed)

 

Flow :

 

-User give vehicle no.

-User give location from displayed available locations where vehicle has travelled. Ex: KT M

-Then, user is asked , Ex: There are 5 cameras installed in KTM.

Did the vehicle pass through C1(y/n)?.

If yes :

                Record all the cameras position ex: C1, C2 where vehicle has passed

Will be asked for other remaining cameras

-After all cameras locations has been asked for the given location, user is asked if the vehicle moved through other locations.

                If yes:

                                Follow steps as KTM

                Else:

                                Record all the movemens  in database.

 

 

Table used: Vehicle_Movement
